name: Buddycards
description: Buddycards is a fun, item collecting mod that adds cards you can find all over your Minecraft world. Currently there are 5 packs containing 54 cards and 1 pack containing 36 cards and you can find them in chests, dungeons and villages!

name: The Legend of Herobrine
description: The Legend of Herobrine mod is a revival of the classic Herobrine mod but with a few new additions. With this mod you need to summon Herobrine into your world with a shrine.

description: Slimier Slimes adds new variations on the slime mob by giving them new abilities and new drops. You‚Äôll notice them immediately from standard slimes since they‚Äôll likely have a different color except for the creeper slime, which can be deceiving since they will explode in much the same way as creepers will. name: GuardsCraft

name: Earth Mobs Mod
description: The Earth Mobs Mod adds a few new mobs and some variations on them and existing mobs to make the world of Minecraft a bit more dynamic and interesting. They can be as simple as muddy pigs, which are really just pigs that fall in mud.

name: Extensive

Here you can harvest molten rock and wood for new blocks to build with. As the biome name suggests, it is full of lava so come prepared!

name: The Cactus Mod

name: Linking Books

name: Tetra

name: Incubation
